Package civitas.celestis.util.container

Interface Container<E>

Type Parameters:
E - The type of element to contain
All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
ObjectContainer
public interface Container<E> extends Serializable
A simple object container with no built-in thread safety. Containers support the usage of null values. Containers can be used to make immutable objects effectively mutable by re-assigning their references within the container object.
